description:
As a coffee buyer
  I want a coffee machine that
  I can put coins in 
  or pay with bank card
  and get a cup of Americano with sugar back
  because I like Americano and crave caffeine.

elements.name: buy Americano with sugar and pay with coins

steps.name: that the machine is plugged in
that water is available
that the machine has enough coffee for a cup
the machine has plastic cups
the machine has enough sugar for a cup
the user presses the "Americano" button
the user presses the "Sugar" button
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user inserts a 0 kr coin
the user inserts a 0 kr coin
the user presses the "Start" button
the user recieves 1 cup of Americano with sugar.

description:
As a coffee buyer
I want a coffee machine that
I can put coins in 
or pay with bank card
and if the machine does not have coffee for a cup
then display shows a warning.

elements.name: Missing coffee for Americano

steps.name: that the machine is plugged in
that water is available
the machine has plastic cups
that the machine does not have enough coffee for a cup
the user presses the "Americano" button
the user does not receive a cup of Americano
the display shows "There is not enough coffee"
